&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;12hugo下载&#34;&gt;1.2Hugo下载
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;前往【&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/gohugoio/hugo/tags&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Hugo Github Tags&lt;/a&gt;】，速度慢可以在&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://wwxh.lanzouv.com/iU2Ua2frujsh&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;这里&lt;/a&gt;下载。选择对应版本下载并解压&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Windows下载版本：&lt;strong&gt;hugo_extended_xxxxx_windows_amd64.zip&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/hugo%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1024&#34;
	height=&#34;226&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/hugo%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD_hu_f079e6580a4ca8b4.png 480w, https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/hugo%E4%B8%8B%E8%BD%BD_hu_94fe182d1262bbd9.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;hugo下载&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;453&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;1087px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;2搭建博客&#34;&gt;2搭建博客
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;21创建博客&#34;&gt;2.1创建博客
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;解压上一步下载的&lt;strong&gt;hugo_extended_xxxxx_windows_amd64.zip&lt;/strong&gt;并复制&lt;strong&gt;hugo.exe&lt;/strong&gt;到自己要建立Blog的文件夹下。以我这里实例为&lt;strong&gt;F:\blog&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/MyBlog.png&#34;
	width=&#34;866&#34;
	height=&#34;174&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/MyBlog_hu_b923abf767092434.png 480w, https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/MyBlog_hu_5a360b2570f7a2e6.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;497&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;1194px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;在&lt;strong&gt;hugo&lt;/strong&gt;所在文件夹的地址栏打出&lt;strong&gt;cmd&lt;/strong&gt;，然后Enter唤起命令行&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/MyBlog2.1.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1001&#34;
	height=&#34;259&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/MyBlog2.1_hu_c5387aa0cb52ab08.png 480w, https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/MyBlog2.1_hu_a7265dc7bad33cd7.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;386&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;927px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;敲出命令&lt;code&gt;hugo new site xxx&lt;/code&gt;创建hugo文件&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/MyBlog2.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1464&#34;
	height=&#34;326&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/MyBlog2_hu_9ff411231002c368.png 480w, https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/MyBlog2_hu_b0f19c6ca84382f8.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;449&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;1077px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;敲出命令&lt;code&gt;cd xxx&lt;/code&gt;进入hugo文件夹（以下称该文件夹为&lt;strong&gt;主文件夹&lt;/strong&gt;），并将hugo.exe文件复制到创建的文件夹内&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/MyBlog3.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1206&#34;
	height=&#34;619&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/MyBlog3_hu_9ff8cfcfc709744e.png 480w, https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/MyBlog3_hu_1ae5e1f3aad30c7c.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;194&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;467px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;敲打命令&lt;code&gt;hugo server -D&lt;/code&gt;启动服务，访问&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;http://localhost:1313/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;http://localhost:1313&lt;/a&gt;，Ctrl+C停止服务 &lt;strong&gt;（hugo默认是没有主题的，需要进行主题配置）&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/MyBlog4.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1200&#34;
	height=&#34;600&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/MyBlog4_hu_6b6da495e2669802.png 480w, https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/MyBlog4_hu_6aaf8547fb21730d.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;200&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;480px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;22配置主题&#34;&gt;2.2配置主题
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;前往【[Hugo Themes](&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://themes.gohugo.io/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Complete List | Hugo Themes (gohugo.io)&lt;/a&gt;)】，查找自己喜欢的主题，进行下载&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/theme1.png&#34;
	width=&#34;1910&#34;
	height=&#34;893&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/theme1_hu_ab9b5a7c331503fb.png 480w, https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/theme1_hu_9c0f6a950465505e.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;213&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;513px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这边以【&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/CaiJimmy/hugo-theme-stack/tags&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Stack主题&lt;/a&gt;】为例，将下载好的主题解压，放到你Blog的&lt;code&gt;/themes&lt;/code&gt;文件夹中&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/theme2.png&#34;
	width=&#34;878&#34;
	height=&#34;380&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/theme2_hu_46f63daa6ac79d8e.png 480w, https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/theme2_hu_85effbed9c0297fe.png 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;231&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;554px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;将&lt;code&gt;exampleSite&lt;/code&gt;样例数据中的 &lt;strong&gt;Content&lt;/strong&gt; 和 &lt;strong&gt;hugo.yaml&lt;/strong&gt; 复制到主文件夹中，并删掉主文件夹下的&lt;code&gt;hugo.toml&lt;/code&gt;和&lt;code&gt;content/post/rich-content&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/theme3.png&#34;
	width=&#34;832&#34;
	height=&#34;458&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/theme3_hu_8b1c460d67777ae.png 480w, https://mqdfei.top/p/hugohugo--github-%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2%E8%87%AA%E5%B7%B1%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2/image/theme3_hu_324ce0f93d2792a0.png 1024w&#34;
